docs.abstract: Talking to children about various types of protest can empower them to make their voices heard.
docs.snippet: Talking to children about various types of protest can empower them to make their voices heard.
docs.lead_paragraph: The spring and early summer of 2020 was a tough time for me and many other parents. The deaths of George Floyd, Breonna Taylor and the spotlight on previous victims such as Elijah McClain broke our hearts again and again as we watched graphic videos of police-involved killings and stayed glued to the news. There were days that I woke up crying and went to bed crying.

headline.main: Baking the World a Better Place

docs.abstract: HBO’s noir prequel has panache and a fine star performance, but it doesn’t entirely make the case for itself.
docs.snippet: HBO’s noir prequel has panache and a fine star performance, but it doesn’t entirely make the case for itself.
docs.lead_paragraph: I would not have expected “Perry Mason” to have any special relevance in the year 2020. The new HBO serial, set in 1931, based on a nearly nine-decade-old Erle Stanley Gardner book series that inspired a classic TV courtroom drama in 1957, is at first blush one more gritty pay-cable bummer about a tormented male antihero and the tough fellas and woeful dames who surround him.

headline.main: Review: ‘Perry Mason’ Returns, Hard-Boiled and Warmed Over
headline.print_headline: At Least the Gritty Streets Are Pretty

docs.abstract: After his breakthrough win in NASCAR’s top series, only the second such victory by a Black driver at that level, Wallace talked about learning to shut out ugly noise and to focus on what matters most.
docs.snippet: After his breakthrough win in NASCAR’s top series, only the second such victory by a Black driver at that level, Wallace talked about learning to shut out ugly noise and to focus on what matters most.
docs.lead_paragraph: Bubba Wallace’s fiancée, Amanda Carter, supplied the positivity. Their Aussiedoodle, Asher, brought the joy. Denny Hamlin and Michael Jordan put Wallace in a fast car, and on Monday he joined Wendell Scott, becoming the second Black driver to win a race at NASCAR’s highest level.

headline.main: Bubba Wallace Is Ebullient, Defiant and Comfortable
headline.print_headline: ‘You Do This to Be the Best’: Wallace  Keeps Focus on Racing and It Pays Off

docs.lead_paragraph: The Rev. Dr. Martin Luther King Jr.’s name has been on a lot of politicians’ and pundits’ lips this June, the most tumultuous month yet in what may be the nation’s most tumultuous year since 1968: the year Dr. King was assassinated.
